aft}}, a Confucian scholar (儒学者/儒生) (born [[1561]]). * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1631]] [[October 7]]） – {{ill|Katō Yoshiaki|ja|加藤嘉明|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, lord of the {{ill|Iyo Matsuyama Domain|ja|伊予松山藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born [[1563]]). * {{ill|Kanbun|ja|寛文|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1664]] [[October 30]]） – {{ill|Nambu Shigenao|ja|南部重直|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 2nd lord of the {{ill|Morioka Domain|ja|盛岡藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born [[1606]]). * {{ill|Shōtoku (era)|ja|正徳|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1711]] [[October 23]]） – {{ill|Matsudaira Masachika|ja|松平昌親|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, lord of the {{ill|Fukui Domain|ja|福井藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born [[1640]]). * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1821]] [[October 7]]） – {{ill|Hanawa Hokiichi|ja|塙保己一|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a scholar of national literature (国文学者) (born [[1746]]).
