== Events == * {{ill|Bun'ei|ja|文永|qq=draft|qq=}} 8th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1271]] [[October 17]]） – {{ill|Nichiren|ja|日蓮|qq=draft|qq=}} was exiled to {{ill|Sado Island|ja|佐渡島|qq=draft|qq=}}. * {{ill|Genki|ja|元亨|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1570]] [[October 11]]） – The 【本願寺 Kōsa】 of the Hongan-ji called on adherents in various provinces to rise up and attack {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|ja|織田信長|qq=draft|qq=}}, thus beginning the decade-long 【Ishiyama War】. * {{ill|Genki|ja|元亨|qq=draft|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1571]] [[September 30]]） – {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|ja|織田信長|qq=draft|qq=}} carried out the 【Mount Hiei Arson Incident】. * {{ill|Meiji era|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1872]] [[October 14]]） – Japan's first formal railway, running between 【Shinbashi】 and 【Yokohama】, was officially opened; service began the following day (【Railway Day】).
== Births ==
== Deaths == * {{ill|Taika|ja|大化|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} [[645]] [[October 7]]） – {{ill|Kobun Daikō Ōkimi|ja|古人大兄皇子|qq=draft|qq=}}, the first son of {{ill|Emperor Jomei|ja|舒明天皇|qq=draft|qq=}} (birth year unknown). * {{ill|Chian (era)|ja|治安|qq=draft|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1022]] [[October 10]]） – {{ill|Tōshi Naishinnō|ja|当子内親王|qq=draft|qq=}}, the first princess of {{ill|Emperor Sanjō|ja|三条天皇|qq=draft|qq=}} (born [[1001]]). * {{ill|Ninji|ja|人治|qq=draft|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1242]] [[October 7]]） – {{ill|Shuntoku Tennō|ja|順徳天皇|qq=draft|qq=}}, the 84th Emperor of Japan (born [[1197]]). * {{ill|Genna|ja|元和|qq=draft|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1619]] [[October 19]]） – {{ill|Fujiwara Sokaka|ja|藤原惺窩|qq=draft|qq=}}, a Confucian scholar (儒学者/儒生) (born [[1561]]). * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1631]] [[October 7]]） – {{ill|Katō Yoshiaki|ja|加藤嘉明|qq=draft|qq=}}, lord of the {{ill|Iyo Matsuyama Domain|ja|伊予松山藩|qq=draft|qq=}} (born [[1563]]). * {{ill|Kanbun|ja|寛文|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1664]] [[October 30]]） – {{ill|Nambu Shigenao|ja|南部重直|qq=draft|qq=}}, the 2nd lord of the {{ill|Morioka Domain|ja|盛岡藩|qq=draft|qq=}} (born [[1606]]). * {{ill|Shōtoku (era)|ja|正徳|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1711]] [[October 23]]） – {{ill|Matsudaira Masachika|ja|松平昌親|qq=draft|qq=}}, lord of the {{ill|Fukui Domain|ja|福井藩|qq=draft|qq=}} (born [[1640]]). * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1821]] [[October 7]]） – {{ill|Hanawa Hokiichi|ja|塙保己一|qq=draft|qq=}}, a scholar of national literature (国文学者) (born [[1746]]).
