manuelle/Shōtoku (era)|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1711]] [[October 23]]） – {{ill|Matsudaira Masachika|ja|松平昌親|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Matsudaira Masachika|qq=}}, lord of the {{ill|Fukui Domain|ja|福井藩|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fukui Domain|qq=}} (born [[1640]]). * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunsei|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1821]] [[October 7]]） – {{ill|Hanawa Hokiichi|ja|塙保己一|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hanawa Hokiichi|qq=}}, a scholar of national literature (国文学者) (born [[1746]]).
