== Deaths == * [[:en:Taika (era)|Taika]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[645]] [[October 7]]） – {{ill|Kobun Daikō Ōkimi|ja|古人大兄皇子|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kobun Daikō Ōkimi|qq=}}, the first son of [[:en:Emperor Jomei|Emperor Jomei]] (birth year unknown). * [[:en:Public security|Chian (era)]] 2nd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[1022]] [[October 10]]） – {{ill|Tōshi Naishinnō|ja|当子内親王|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tōshi Naishinnō|qq=}}, the first princess of [[:en:Emperor Sanjō|Emperor Sanjō]] (born [[1001]]). * {{ill|Ninji|ja|人治|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ninji|qq=}} 3rd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[1242]] [[October 7]]） – [[:en:Emperor Juntoku|Shuntoku Tennō]], the 84th Emperor of Japan (born [[1197]]). * [[:en:Yuanhe|Genna]] 5th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1619]] [[October 19]]） – [[:en:Fujiwara Seika|Fujiwara Sokaka]], a Confucian scholar (儒学者/儒生) (born [[1561]]). * [[:en:Kan'ei|Kan'ei]] 8th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1631]] [[October 7]]） – [[:en:Katō Yoshiaki|Katō Yoshiaki]], lord of the [[:en:Iyo-Matsuyama Domain|Iyo Matsuyama Domain]] (born [[1563]]). * [[:en:Kanbun (era)|Kanbun]] 4th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1664]] [[October 30]]） – [[:en:Nanbu Shigenao|Nambu Shigenao]], the 2nd lord of the [[:en:Morioka Domain|Morioka Domain]] (born [[1606]]). * [[:en:正德|Shōtoku (era)]] 1st year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1711]] [[October 23]]） – [[:en:Matsudaira Masachika|Matsudaira Masachika]], lord of the [[:en:Fukui Domain|Fukui Domain]] (born [[1640]]). * [[:en:Bunsei|Bunsei]] 4th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1821]] [[October 7]]） – [[:en:Hanawa Hokiichi|Hanawa Hokiichi]], a scholar of national literature (国文学者) (born [[1746]]).
